===Come here, there's a reward===
{{Messages|text=
:'''The Herta:''' Come here, there's a reward
:{Choice} What's the job?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' How much is the pay? I don't take just any job
:{Choice} My rates have gone up
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What are we testing now? My rates have gone up, just so you know
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Receiving attachment ''New Clothes Shopping List and Storage Guide''
:{{DIcon|Warning}} File too large. Unable to download
:'''The Herta:''' Hurry up and upgrade your messaging system
:'''The Herta:''' Let's just say I got some new clothes, and the puppets alone can't keep up with organizing them
:{Choice} How many did you buy?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' How many clothes did you buy? Give me one!
:{Choice} Give it to me
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm (Trailblazer). Give me some
