:'''The Herta:''' I bought it for the puppets
:{Choice} The puppet's clothes?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Do puppets need to change clothes too?
::'''The Herta:''' Of course, with such a gorgeous face on them, who could've resisted buying pretty clothes for them
:{Choice} I'm the only one without new clothes to wear
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Darn it, even the puppet has more clothes than I do
::'''The Herta:''' Oh, so you finally figured it out
:'''The Herta:''' There are too many styles to count, so remember to sort them by category when organizing them
:'''The Herta:''' Stylish at first glance, obviously something I'd wear, easy to spot. Let's sort these first
:'''The Herta:''' Ruan Mei keeps recommending the same few things over and over, just put them together with the ones above
:'''The Herta:''' The more eye-searing the color scheme is, the more it belongs in the retro section
:'''The Herta:''' The harder it is to describe and understand the pattern, the more it belongs in haute couture
:'''The Herta:''' As for the rest, just refer to the guide yourself
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend has sent their location
:'''The Herta:''' I sent you the wardrobe's location. Should be close to your coordinates
:'''The Herta:''' There's a small space station right there
:'''The Herta:''' Don't worry about not having enough space
:{Choice} Where? A space station!?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Where? A space station? Does Asta know about that?
:{Choice} Does Asta know about this?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You bought a space station wardrobe for the puppets? Does Asta know about this?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I need the payment first, then I'll get started
:'''The Herta:''' As for the rest, that's her problem
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your call is now being transferred to your friend Asta
